01:27:46.106 --> 01:27:47.869
Let's get this done with.

01:27:48.075 --> 01:27:50.566
Over the edge you go, boys.

01:27:50.777 --> 01:27:51.835
- Wait!
- Shut up.

01:27:52.045 --> 01:27:53.603
Wait, sheriff. Wait, wait, wait.

01:27:53.814 --> 01:27:57.978
- Sheriff, I'm gonna shoot them now.
- No, no, let's listen to this.

01:27:58.185 --> 01:27:59.948
Look,

01:28:00.954 --> 01:28:03.445
you and I, we're cut
from the same cloth.

01:28:03.690 --> 01:28:05.624
I mean, we're a lot alike,
don't you think?

01:28:05.859 --> 01:28:10.387
Yeah, sure, I'm better with numbers
and I bathe often.

01:28:10.597 --> 01:28:15.330
I have a dental plan that allows me
to keep all my teeth, unlike yourself.

01:28:18.472 --> 01:28:20.497
- Yeah?
- I learned a little something

01:28:20.707 --> 01:28:24.609
the last couple days, getting chased
by ass-face and dick-chin there.

01:28:24.811 --> 01:28:26.176
And that is...

01:28:26.413 --> 01:28:29.143
I have two of the best friends
anyone could ever ask for.

01:28:29.349 --> 01:28:32.011
I've got the love of a good woman.

01:28:32.219 --> 01:28:35.882
I've got a really good life.
I mean, I've got an amazing life.

01:28:37.257 --> 01:28:41.057
And I've decided that my life's
worth living. Now, you have to decide

01:28:41.261 --> 01:28:44.560
if your life's worth living too,
because if it is,

01:28:45.265 --> 01:28:47.096
you put your gun down.

01:28:47.634 --> 01:28:49.033
And if we don't?

01:28:51.738 --> 01:28:54.536
- Bye, bye, boys.
- It's go time.

01:28:54.741 --> 01:28:57.801
- Do this to him.
- Put the pin back in the grenade.

01:28:58.011 --> 01:29:00.502
- That is my grenade, sir.
- The plan was for me to sacrifice

01:29:00.714 --> 01:29:03.205
myself if need be
while you two ran for it.

01:29:03.417 --> 01:29:04.679
- I didn't know.
- My grenade...

01:29:04.885 --> 01:29:07.581
- I'm not a mind reader, Jerry.
- Give me back my grenade.

01:29:12.292 --> 01:29:13.816
Run!

01:29:14.795 --> 01:29:16.057
It's gonna blow!

01:29:27.207 --> 01:29:28.834
All right, that's it. You're dead.

01:29:29.042 --> 01:29:31.875
When all this is over, someone's
buying the first round. Not it.

01:29:32.079 --> 01:29:34.343
- Not it.
- Enough of this shit. Just shoot them.

01:29:34.548 --> 01:29:36.448
Do you think there's beer in heaven?

01:29:37.384 --> 01:29:38.783
I was thinking about the bar
in town.

01:30:03.143 --> 01:30:05.611
- Let's get off this mountain.
- All right.

01:30:08.181 --> 01:30:13.676
These charges are "unsubstantuated"
and "injustifigurable" and...

01:30:13.887 --> 01:30:17.254
That's right. We did it.
How you like me now?

01:30:17.457 --> 01:30:20.085
This is the scene here
at police headquarters

01:30:20.293 --> 01:30:23.319
as three local heroes emerge
to a cheering crowd.

01:30:23.530 --> 01:30:26.624
The men accidentally helped break up
one of the biggest drug rings

01:30:26.833 --> 01:30:30.769
in state history while hiking
in a remote section of the Cascades.

01:30:30.970 --> 01:30:33.234
My old man would not believe this.

01:30:33.640 --> 01:30:36.200
- Billy wouldn't believe it.
- Actually, know what?

01:30:36.409 --> 01:30:37.774
I think he would.

01:30:38.178 --> 01:30:42.274
Oh, my goodness.
Look at this ensemble. I like it.

01:30:42.482 --> 01:30:43.915
- Look at you.
- Thank you, boys.

01:30:44.117 --> 01:30:45.914
Look at this stud. Del!

01:30:46.119 --> 01:30:48.417
No names. Fuzz.

01:30:48.955 --> 01:30:53.016
Glad I caught you guys before you
headed out. I got something for you.

01:30:53.426 --> 01:30:54.552
What's this?

01:30:54.994 --> 01:30:58.088
- D.B.'s parachute. Are you sure?
- Damn sure.

01:30:58.298 --> 01:31:00.596
There's a little something for you
rolled up inside there too.

01:31:00.800 --> 01:31:02.700
- Thank you.
- So where you headed?

01:31:02.902 --> 01:31:05.837
Thought I'd see the world.
I might even hit Washington.

01:31:06.706 --> 01:31:09.140
Wow. One state over.

01:31:09.342 --> 01:31:13.073
Till I do, I'm just telling tall tales.

01:31:17.283 --> 01:31:21.344
Remember, carry your friends
wherever you go.

01:31:21.721 --> 01:31:23.154
Close to your heart.

01:31:23.890 --> 01:31:26.688
Or on your back.
I got D.B.'s bones in my satchel.

01:31:27.560 --> 01:31:29.755
Thought I'd give him a proper burial.

01:31:30.964 --> 01:31:35.230
I spent 30 years
waiting to have a life.

01:31:37.937 --> 01:31:40.872
- What the hell?
- Oh, my gosh.

01:31:41.107 --> 01:31:42.506
Oh, my God.

01:31:43.676 --> 01:31:44.700
D.B. Didn't burn it all.

01:31:45.545 --> 01:31:47.809
He couldn't. It was Del's share.

01:31:48.047 --> 01:31:49.810
There's gotta be 100 grand in here.

01:31:50.016 --> 01:31:52.507
We'll split it three ways.

01:31:52.752 --> 01:31:54.617
One-third, one-third, one-third?

01:31:55.488 --> 01:31:57.115
You know what?

01:31:58.324 --> 01:32:01.122
No, thanks. I'm...

01:32:01.327 --> 01:32:02.726
- I'm good.
- I'm not good.

01:32:02.962 --> 01:32:04.395
You guys split it.

01:32:05.265 --> 01:32:07.256
You wanna split it? Fifty-fifty?

01:32:08.535 --> 01:32:10.298
Actually, I can't.

01:32:10.503 --> 01:32:13.904
Because I bet you 100 grand
that you couldn't catch a salmon

01:32:14.107 --> 01:32:16.302
with a flashlight and I lost.

01:32:16.543 --> 01:32:20.138
Besides, Tom, you got bills to pay.
You got a new life to start.

01:32:20.713 --> 01:32:21.702
I don't know what to say.

01:32:22.949 --> 01:32:24.250
Just say we're square.

01:32:25.751 --> 01:32:29.016
No, actually, we're not square.

01:32:30.222 --> 01:32:33.988
I seem to recall a certain part
of that wager being one left nut,

01:32:34.193 --> 01:32:36.525
and I'm gonna get it.
Come on, pleated pants, let's go.

01:32:36.729 --> 01:32:38.629
- Hey, Tom. Hey. Hey.
- Oh, no.

01:32:39.064 --> 01:32:40.531
Don't make me go in
through the throat.

01:32:40.733 --> 01:32:43.099
- I'm going through the throat.
- You said I could keep it.

01:32:43.302 --> 01:32:45.202
- No, I didn't.
- Tom, you said I could keep it.

01:32:45.571 --> 01:32:47.038
Jerry! Officer!

01:32:48.674 --> 01:32:51.268
<i>Hi. This is Jerry, and I can't
come to the phone right now,</i>

01:32:51.477 --> 01:32:54.446
<i>because I am busy trying
to convince the love of my life</i>

01:32:54.647 --> 01:32:55.807
<i>to give me another chance.</i>

01:32:56.015 --> 01:32:58.540
<i>And I will prove to her
that I grew up just enough</i>

01:32:58.751 --> 01:33:01.720
<i>to know that I want the responsibility,
day in and day out,</i>

01:33:01.920 --> 01:33:03.945
<i>of being there for her
in this relationship,</i>

01:33:04.156 --> 01:33:07.648
<i>which I am hoping will someday
become marriage and kids</i>

01:33:07.860 --> 01:33:10.988
<i>and a long and unbelievably
happy life together.</i>

01:33:11.430 --> 01:33:12.829
Hi, honey.

01:33:37.756 --> 01:33:40.224
So happy right now.

01:33:41.093 --> 01:33:45.029
That was really, really beautiful.

01:33:50.402 --> 01:33:54.099
- Will you get the light, hon?
- Oh, yeah.

01:33:56.608 --> 01:33:59.099
You're so good at that now.

01:34:01.313 --> 01:34:04.840
And then I jumped on the grenade
to save my buddies and...

01:34:05.050 --> 01:34:07.280
Blew my rib cage all to shit.

01:34:07.486 --> 01:34:09.613
Sent me 156 feet in the air.

01:34:09.822 --> 01:34:13.553
Then I went back and paid off
all my debts in full with D.B.'s money.

01:34:17.162 --> 01:34:18.288
One question.

01:34:19.665 --> 01:34:21.326
What's a downstairs?

